ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/253150/extras/3a435fddffd18ef14aeb192d88eb9ce1.poster.avif?t=1768327449\" width=780 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/253150/extras/3a435fddffd18ef14aeb192d88eb9ce1.webm?t=1768327449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/253150/extras/3a435fddffd18ef14aeb192d88eb9ce1.mp4?t=1768327449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/253150/extras/4f06079cb9e3305b1ecb099f4dc5c57f.webp?t=1768327449\" width=610 height=63 /></span></p>",
